overview: On April 23rd GCW presents The Old Me live on FITE! The event features collision of the two legends - Minoru Suzuki and 2 Cold Scorpio.  Also in the lineup:  JWM vs Hoodfoot  The Briscoes vs SGC (High Incident)  Bandido vs Joey Janela  Alex Shelley vs Nick Wayne  Chris Dickinson vs ACH  Team Bussy vs ASF & Gringo Loco  Alex Colon vs AJ Gray  ... and more!
title: GCW: The Old Me
